data.description: Absolutely Charming Country Cottage, situated on 5 wooded acres near Pecan Bend South Subdivision! Gorgeous 1 Story, 3Bed/2Bath, 20x20 shop with lean-to, and Generac Generator!! Enter to luxury vinyl plank throughout the entire home & recent paint! You will love the The Kitchen w/ GRANITE counters, Tons of Cabinets Providing Ample Storage Space for Your Kitchen Gadgets. Living, kitchen, & dining/breakfast rooms all flow seamlessly together allowing you to entertain to the max or enjoy intimate setting around dining/breakfast room! The Master Bath Has "His & Hers" sinks, Large Separate Shower and Farm House Door Closet! Retreat after a long day on the deck enjoying Spectacular views of giant oak trees& free roaming deer! LOW TAXES! Don't miss your chance to own this amazing home! Country living at its finest! Roof 2017, A/C 2017, All Appliances 3-5 years new! This property combines country comfort with city conveniences near by, just minutes from major freeways like 288 & FM 762!
